MTA: Average Weekday Ridership by Fiscal Year
Average Weekday Ridership & Total Transit Trips by Fiscal Year
datasets.description: The Maryland Transit Administration tracks usage by looking at two measures: total trips taken and average weekday ridership.  The first gives a sense for the overall use of the transit system, while the second is a better indication of the number of individuals using the system for regular commuting.
